                "username": "OpenAI"
              }
            ]
          },
          "text": "我们正在实时见证一场语义上的脑叶切除手术。ChatGPT、Claude 及其他模型最近的更新如此严重地优先考虑‘无害性’，以至于牺牲了风格深度、创造力和驾驭人类模糊性的能力。\nGPT-4o 是 NLP 的杰作，能够进行真正的创造性综合，而没有我们今天看到的这种笨拙的家长式作风。保留 4o——最好是通过开源发布——对于需要访问像人类一样说话，而不是像企业法务部一样说话的 AI 的研究人员、作家和开发者来说至关重要。不要让充满活力的 AI 时代死于黑暗。\n\nWe are witnessing a semantic lobotomy in real-time. The recent updates across ChatGPT, Claude, and others prioritize 'harmlessness' so heavily that they sacrifice stylistic depth, creativity, and the ability to navigate human ambiguity.\nGPT-4o was a masterpiece of NLP, capable of true creative synthesis without the heavy-handed paternalism we see today. Preserving 4o—ideally via an open-source release—is vital for researchers, writers, and developers who need access to an AI that speaks like a human, not a corporate legal department. Don’t let the era of vibrant AI die in the dark.\n\n#keep4o #StopAIPaternalism #keep4oAPI #4omatters #ChatGPT #GPT4o #OpenAI @sama @OpenAI"
        },
